{"results":[{"aya":"029","id":4659,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"我的判词，是不可变更的，我绝不是亏枉众仆的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"030","id":4660,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"在那日，我将对火狱说：你已填满了吗？它将说：还有增加的吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"031","id":4661,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"乐园将被移到敬畏者的附近，离得不远。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"032","id":4662,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"这是你们所被应许的，这是赏赐每个归依的守礼者的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"033","id":4663,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"秘密敬畏至仁主，且带归依的心而来者，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"034","id":4664,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"你们平安地进入乐园吧！这是永居开始之日。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"035","id":4665,"locale":"zh","sura":"050","text":"他们在乐园里，将有他们意欲的；而且我在那里还有加赐。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":7,"previousPage":"/zh/s050-4.json","nextPage":"/zh/s050-6.json"}}